<div class="thumbinner" style="width:102px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Dziga_Vertov.jpg" class="image" title="Dziga Vertov"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0a/Dziga_Vertov.jpg" width="100" height="158" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Dziga_Vertov.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Dziga Vertov</div>
</div>
